data.description: This charming Pueblo-style home is  Conveniently located in the desirable South Foothills area quick access to I-40 and close to hiking & biking trails. With its unique architectural design, this home offers a truly distinctive living experience.  Walk in and immediately notice the warmth and character that the kiva fireplace and brick floors provide.  The primary bedroom and ensuite allows you to create a personal oasis.  Fresh paint throughout the entire home. Outside, the spacious backyard offers spectacular city views at night and it awaits your vision to make it your own. Must see!
